NAME
	send_atomic_message - send message that can be retrieved after rollback

SYNOPSIS
	void send_atomic_message(string message)


DESCRIPTION
	Add a string to the list of messages that can be retrieved after an
	atomic rollback occurs.

ERRORS
	If the message starts with the character "*" and also contains a \0
	character, an error will result.  A \0 character elsewhere in the
	message is not rejected.

SEE ALSO
	efun/retrieve_atomic_messages
